public abstract class MessageChannel

Message channel abstraction for the SIP stack.

Version:
1.2 $Revision: 1.40 $ $Date: 2010-12-02 22:44:53 $
Author:
M. Ranganathan
Contains additions for support of symmetric NAT contributed by Hagai.
